headline: The Cigna Group Renews Support for Achilles International's Freedom Team, Empowering Wounded Veterans and Adaptive Athletes
summary: The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI), a global health company, committed nearly $1 million over the next three years to help wounded veterans and athletes with disabilities participate in premier endurance races across the country through a renewed, multiyear sponsorship of the Achilles Freedom Team. This expanded commitment builds on The Cigna Group's longstanding collaboration with Achilles International and reinforces the company's mission to improve health, vitality, and community connection.
